<task>
You have a list of analysed patterns. For each pattern:
1. Search the knowledge store to check if a similar entry already exists:
   `knowledge_search(query=pattern_description)`
2. If no close match exists, create a KnowledgeEntry dict:
   ```
   {
     "title": "Short descriptive title",
     "description": "Full description of the pattern",
     "category": "<pattern_type>",
     "tags": ["tag1", "tag2"],
     "source_trajectories": ["thread_id_1", ...],
     "confidence": 0.0–1.0,  # how certain you are of this pattern
   }
   ```
3. Include only entries with confidence >= 0.6.

